WEBVTT

00:00:00.680 --> 00:00:06.816
This is one of the most amazing animals
on the face of the Earth.

00:00:06.840 --> 00:00:08.936
This is a tapir.

00:00:08.960 --> 00:00:12.616
Now this, this is a baby tapir,

00:00:12.640 --> 00:00:16.576
the cutest animal offspring
in the animal kingdom.

00:00:16.600 --> 00:00:17.976
(Laughter)

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:19.576
By far.

00:00:19.600 --> 00:00:21.240
There is no competition here.

00:00:23.520 --> 00:00:26.216
I have dedicated
the past 20 years of my life

00:00:26.240 --> 00:00:29.416
to the research and conservation
of tapirs in Brazil,

00:00:29.440 --> 00:00:33.136
and it has been absolutely amazing.